{"tid":842371,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"bio撚入 扯旗嘅時候點解會無曬腰痛感覺？","createTime":"2018-09-30T09:06:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-30T11:44:20.000Z","uid":82450,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"f09dd5b3628a482d4ed2081a22ec3cf54a33f3df","tid":842371,"uid":82450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T09:06:23.000Z","msg":"事關我返工差唔多坐足全日，晚晚訓覺嘅時候都會覺得又緊又痛，zip枕頭打側訓都試過無用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n之後有次look連登見到j圖，扯咗旗就發現冇咁痛，一覺訓到大天光<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔知到底係咩原因呢？<br />\n<br />\n讀bio嘅人如果解釋到依個現象嘅原因，相信你幾大機會拎到諾背爾獎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d96b87e36f8f89d2b0dfedace670ce1338402914","tid":842371,"uid":82450,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T09:12:43.000Z","msg":"唔信？<br />\n<br />\n直刻貼張j圖俾你地試下<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://66.media.tumblr.com/441c3bebdda7d068c52097eb495e194e/tumblr_pdqvjfSEa21xojr6ro1_400.gif \" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F66.media.tumblr.com%2F441c3bebdda7d068c52097eb495e194e%2Ftumblr_pdqvjfSEa21xojr6ro1_400.gif%20&h=3b167cb4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"feb75a967488278efca558b33220a06b1de791da","tid":842371,"uid":94828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T09:13:15.000Z","msg":"下身血液流通啲"},{"pid":"1e3a3c30610671bbf7886e88e65d9b25be3eb1b8","tid":842371,"uid":82450,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"feb75a967488278efca558b33220a06b1de791da","tid":842371,"uid":94828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T09:13:15.000Z","msg":"下身血液流通啲"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T09:18:11.000Z","msg":"點會咁簡單 咁樣我做幾下深蹲 跳幾下繩都得啦<br />\n<br />\n你立刻訓低 扯過旗感受一下再答<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://66.media.tumblr.com/76a3d7cd25bf7ee6d6c031060fcc5fb7/tumblr_pdqshrNcOr1xojr6ro1_500.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F